PORTLAND, Ore. â€“ The 6A volleyball regular season came to a close Thursday night and the playoff field has been determined. 
Four teams from each of the six leagues earn automatic berths. The next four highest ranked teams by the OSAA earn at-large berths and are safely in the postseason. The next eight highest ranked teams will compete in play-in games, with the four winners earning a playoff berth.
